GG_Village
By Harlequiine

My most popular gungame map.
I aimed to make a different kind of churches, and I think I succeeded.
This is a very undetailed map, almost no entities, just plain walls and floors, but it's very fun.
There's a range of close up & long range shooting, and some camping spots.
It will end up on your server map rotation list if you give it a try.

Recommended for 8-16 players.
